                  stellar stream, although no individual members of the stream
                  have previously been identified. Using both BHBs and more
                  numerous red giant branch stars cross-matched to
                  $\textit\{Gaia\}$ Data Release 2, we identify extended tidal
                  tails from NGC 5466 that are both spatially and kinematically
                  coherent. Interestingly, we find that this stream does not
                  follow the same path as the previous detection at large
