                  31$^\{\circ\}$ of sky and show that it exhibits a very strong
                  distance gradient ranging from 10 $<$ R$_\{helio\}$ $<$ 30
                  kpc. We compare our observations to simple dynamical models
                  of the stream and find that they are able to broadly
                  reproduce the overall path and kinematics. The fact that NGC
